title: Week In Politics: Hillary Clinton's Presidential Campaign
teaser: NPR's Audie Cornish speaks with regular political commentators David Brooks of The New York Times and E.J. Dionne of the Washington Post and Brookings Institution about Hillary Clinton's presidential campaign, and how it differs from the campaigns of her husband.
